vote.title: An ordinance granting a revocable license to OUTFRONT Media LLC, for the use of approximately 1,020 square feet of aerial space to occupy, maintain and utilize a videoboard sign over a portion of Cesar Chavez Boulevard right-of-way near its intersection with Elm Street - Revenue: General Fund $6,633.00 annually, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
